## 7. 패킷 직렬화 바이트 레이아웃

### 공통 헤더
```
[0..3] int32 (little-endian) : 페이로드 길이 + 1 (타입 포함)
[4]    byte                  : PacketType
[5..N] byte[]                : 페이로드
```

### AUTH_CHALLENGE (0x03)
```
[0..31] byte[32] : nonce
```

### AUTH_REQUEST (0x01)
```
[0..31] byte[32] : SHA256 해시
```

### AUTH_RESPONSE (0x02)
```
[0]    byte   : success (0/1)
[1..2] ushort : screenWidth
[3..4] ushort : screenHeight
```

### SCREEN_FULL (0x10)
```
[0..1] ushort   : width
[2..3] ushort   : height
[4..N] byte[]   : JPEG 데이터
```

### MOUSE_MOVE (0x20)
```
[0..3] float : normalizedX
[4..7] float : normalizedY
```

### MOUSE_CLICK (0x21)
```
[0..3] float : normalizedX
[4..7] float : normalizedY
[8]    byte  : button (0=좌, 1=우, 2=중)
[9]    byte  : isDown (0/1)
```

### MOUSE_SCROLL (0x22)
```
[0..3] float : normalizedX
[4..7] float : normalizedY
[8..9] short : delta
```

### KEY_EVENT (0x30)
```
[0..1] ushort : virtualKeyCode
[2..3] ushort : scanCode
[4]    byte   : isDown (0/1)
[5]    byte   : isExtended (0/1)
```

### HEARTBEAT (0xF0)
```
(페이로드 없음)
```

